Nollywood actress, Caroline Danjuma has revealed reasons her marriage to the younger brother of Nigeria’s former Defence Minister, General TY Danjuma, did not work. Speaking in the latest episode of reality show, ‘Real Housewives of Lagos’, Danjuma said contrary to rumours, she married her ex-husband for love not money adding that Linda Ikeji is also responsible for her broken marriage. Caroline said, “Part of the reasons why my marriage broke was because of Linda Ikeji. I reached out to her when she wrote some things but she didn’t care. “I married my ex-husband for love not money and I still love him till date. “I’m a perfectionist; I wanted and I’ve always wanted a home. Nobody ever wants a divorce, not even me.” Recall that Caroline’s marriage to Danjuma crashed in 2016.